    <p style="clear: both;"><b>One important thing.</b> Because of the way my payment provider operates, I need the money to be on my account before December 1st, so <strong>this offer ends on November 30th</strong>. After that date, I'll remove this page.</p>
    <p>So, if you do love Chpokk and plan to use it actively, it's a good idea to pay a little bit in advance. Just remember that you have to do it before the 30th of November, and you'll still have more than 15 days to get your money back in case you change your mind.</p>
